==Song information==
* "We Could Walk Together" - from [[Fierce Panda]] compilation, November 1997
* "Five Day Morning" - Pointy Records 7" single, June 1998
* "Reflections After Jane" / "An Hour Before The Light" - Johnny Kane Records 7" single, March 1999
* "Lacewings" / "Saturday" - Motorway Records 7" single, September 1999
* "I Had To Say This" / "Monday's Rain" - Pointy Records 7" single, December 1999
* "(I Want You) More Than Ever" - Elefant Records 7" single, February 2000
* "Rain" / "Joseph Cornell" / "Bicycles" / "As Night Is Falling" - previously unreleased

